- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper involves training and fine-tuning a model. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper involves the use of neural networks. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is unlikely as the paper does not focus on image or video processing, but it cannot be completely ruled out as the Transformer model has also been used in computer vision tasks.
